&lt;h2 id=&#34;Reliable-Prediction&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Reliable-Prediction&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Reliable Prediction&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Reliable Prediction&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Romano, Yaniv, Evan Patterson, and Emmanuel Candes. “Conformalized quantile regression.” &lt;em&gt;Advances in neural information processing systems&lt;/em&gt; 32 (2019). &lt;a href=&#34;https://proceedings.neurips.cc/paper/2019/hash/5103c3584b063c431bd1268e9b5e76fb-Abstract.html&#34;&gt;source&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/yromano/cqr&#34;&gt;code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
